20 ARTICLE, ON:
21 (I) THE INFORMATION REQUIRED UNDER PARAGRAPHS (1) AND
22 (2) OF THIS SUBSECTION BY JUNE 30, 2026, AND EACH YEAR THEREAFTER; AND
23 (II) THE WORK PLAN REQUIRED UNDER PARAGRAPH (3) OF THIS
24 SUBSECTION BY JUNE 30, 2026.
